---
title: Mediterranean Tender Beef & Risoni Stew with Pre-Cut Veggies & Parsley
description: We love a slow cooker dish - Add all your ingredients, and come back later to a meal that is sure to be warm, hearty and comforting. This one involves a rich beef ragu with risoni to keep you satisfied. We can’t wait to dig in!
